  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Box Hustle is a challenging 3D isometric puzzle game inspired by the classic Sokoban. Test your wits as you push wooden crates onto their target spots in levels designed to challenge your logic and planning skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566780/extras/d8fd7a43e23655def5b9825b1113bc97.poster.avif?t=1745666363\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566780/extras/d8fd7a43e23655def5b9825b1113bc97.webm?t=1745666363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566780/extras/d8fd7a43e23655def5b9825b1113bc97.mp4?t=1745666363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every move matter, one wrong step can block your path and force you to rethink your strategy. Do you have what it takes to conquer 100 levels spread across three unique worlds?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566780/extras/efb92adf472e3469c6531e79643b28a3.avif?t=1745666363\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566780/extras_big/efb92adf472e3469c6531e79643b28a3.avif?t=1745666363 width=800 height=295 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Success lies in thinking before you move. Can you master Box Hustle and become the best?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566780/extras/d5849fd1c7d785bf15c98273e367bbbd.avif?t=1745666363\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566780/extras_big/d5849fd1c7d785bf15c98273e367bbbd.avif?t=1745666363 width=800 height=117 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Box Hustle is a challenging 3D isometric puzzle game inspired by the classic Sokoban. Test your wits as you push wooden crates onto their target spots in levels designed to challenge your logic and planning skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566780/extras/d8fd7a43e23655def5b9825b1113bc97.poster.avif?t=1745666363\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566780/extras/d8fd7a43e23655def5b9825b1113bc97.webm?t=1745666363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566780/extras/d8fd7a43e23655def5b9825b1113bc97.mp4?t=1745666363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every move matter, one wrong step can block your path and force you to rethink your strategy. Do you have what it takes to conquer 100 levels spread across three unique worlds?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566780/extras/efb92adf472e3469c6531e79643b28a3.avif?t=1745666363\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566780/extras_big/efb92adf472e3469c6531e79643b28a3.avif?t=1745666363 width=800 height=295 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Success lies in thinking before you move. Can you master Box Hustle and become the best?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566780/extras/d5849fd1c7d785bf15c98273e367bbbd.avif?t=1745666363\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566780/extras_big/d5849fd1c7d785bf15c98273e367bbbd.avif?t=1745666363 width=800 height=117 /></span></p>",
